              'text': 'Download models only from Hugging Face (huggingface.co) or the official Ollama library. On Hugging Face, each file shows a SHA256 hash вҖ” verify it with `sha256sum <model_file>` after downloading. Stick to models from known publishers: Meta, Google, Microsoft, Mistral AI, and Qwen/Alibaba. Avoid anonymous file shares or Discord file drops.',
