      seoTitle: 'Best Long Context Local LLMs April 2026: 128K on Ollama',
      intro: 'Most local LLMs in 2026 support 128K token context windows вҖ” but Ollama defaults to 2048 tokens unless you configure it. As of April 2026, Llama 3.3 70B, Qwen2.5 72B, and Mistral Small 3.1 all support 128K context, with practical reliable limits of 32KвҖ“64K tokens. A 7B model at Q4_K_M needs 14 GB RAM at 128K context vs 6 GB at 4K вҖ” the KV cache doubles your RAM requirement. This guide covers which models work, how to set context length in Ollama, and the RAM required at every context tier.',
